items.name: Espresso Coffee
items.description: "Intensely flavorful espresso: a bold, aromatic pick-me-up crafted for true coffee aficionados. Savor the essence of perfection in every sip."

items.name: Cappuccino Coffee
items.description: Indulge in the rich harmony of espresso, velvety steamed milk, and a frothy crown of foam in our classic Cappuccino. Elevate your coffee experience, one sip at a time.

items.name: Cafe Latte Coffee
items.description: "Indulge in the creamy richness of our signature Cafe Latte, crafted with expertly blended espresso and velvety steamed milk. Taste where every moment is a latte-lover's delight."

items.name: Cafe Mocha Coffee
items.description: Indulge in the rich harmony of espresso and velvety chocolate with our Café Mocha. Every sip, a symphony of flavor to savor. "Sip. Savor. Repeat."

items.name: Flat White Coffee
items.description: "Indulge in the smooth harmony of espresso and velvety microfoam in our Flat White - the epitome of coffee elegance."

items.name: Americano Coffee
items.description: "A bold espresso-based beverage with hot water, offering a smooth and robust flavor profile. Wake up your taste buds with every sip."

items.name: V60 Pour Over Coffee
items.description: "Indulge in the exquisite art of coffee brewing with our Hot V60 Pour Over, crafting rich flavors sip by sip. Elevate your morning ritual with precision and passion, one pour at a time."

items.name: V60 Iced Pour Over Coffee
items.description: Experience the refreshing chill of V60 Iced Pour Over, where smooth coffee meets the cool embrace of ice, delivering a crisp and invigorating taste. Embrace the perfect blend of chill and thrill with every sip. #ChillAndThrill

items.name: Cold Brew Coffee
items.description: A smooth and refreshing coffee delight, crafted by steeping coarse coffee grounds in cold water for an extended period, resulting in a velvety brew with low acidity and subtle, nuanced flavors, perfect for a cool and invigorating caffeine fix.

items.name: Cold Brew Tonic Coffee
items.description: Elevate your refreshment with Cold Brew Tonic, a harmonious blend of smooth, bold cold brew coffee and crisp tonic water, creating a revitalizing beverage with a delightful balance of flavors and a subtle caffeine kick.

items.name: Espresso Tonic Coffee
items.description: Experience the invigorating fusion of intense espresso and crisp tonic water, resulting in a refreshing and sophisticated beverage with a delightful balance of bitterness and effervescence, perfect for a unique coffee experience.

items.name: Iced Mocha Coffee
items.description: "A harmonious blend of rich espresso and creamy chocolate, chilled to perfection for a refreshing indulgence. Sip into satisfaction, one frosty sip at a time."

items.name: Affogato Coffee
items.description: Indulge in the rich harmony of espresso poured over creamy vanilla ice cream in our Affogato Iced Coffee—a divine blend of chill and charm. Savor the marriage of espresso and gelato, where every sip is a symphony of flavor.

items.name: Signature Hot Chocolate
items.description: Indulge in the rich decadence of our Signature Hot Chocolate, crafted with 54% cocoa for a velvety-smooth experience that's simply irresistible. Sip your way to cocoa bliss and elevate your mood, one delightful cup at a time!

items.name: Nutella Hot Chocolate
items.description: Indulge in the rich decadence of Nutella Hot Chocolate, boasting a velvety blend of 54% cocoa perfection. It's the ultimate hug in a mug, guaranteed to sweeten even the chilliest of days!

items.name: Salted Caramel Hot Chocolate
items.description: Indulge in the decadent fusion of rich 54% cocoa with luscious salted caramel, creating a heavenly symphony of flavors. Sip, savor, and let every warm, comforting drop remind you that life is sweet with a dash of salt.

items.name: Tiramisu Hot Chocolate
items.description: Indulge in the decadent fusion of velvety Tiramisu, rich caramel, and smooth 54% cocoa, in a lusciously satisfying hot chocolate. Sip into bliss as each creamy sip unveils the ultimate sweet escape, leaving your taste buds dancing in delight.

items.name: Papa Bears Mix Chocolate
items.description: Indulge in the rich, velvety goodness of Papa Bear's Mix Hot Chocolate, crafted with a luscious 54% cocoa blend. Experience the warmth of every sip, embracing the perfect harmony of sweetness and depth. Embrace the cozy comfort of cocoa perfection.

items.name: Classic Frappe
items.description: Escape to a blissful oasis with the Classic Frappe, where smooth espresso meets icy perfection, blended with velvety milk and a hint of sweetness, offering a refreshing and invigorating coffee indulgence on any sunny day.

items.name: Irish Frappe
items.description: Embark on a decadent journey with Irish Frappe, where velvety coffee meets the smooth embrace of Irish cream liqueur, creating a delightful chilled treat that whispers of indulgence with every sip.

items.name: Hazelnut Frappe
items.description: Indulge in the creamy decadence of a hazelnut frappe, where velvety hazelnut essence meets icy sweetness, creating a refreshing yet satisfying treat that tantalizes the taste buds with its nutty richness and frosty allure.

items.name: Vanilla Frappe
items.description: Escape into creamy decadence with a Vanilla Frappe, where smooth vanilla meets chilled indulgence, creating a heavenly blend of sweetness and refreshment in every frosty sip.

items.name: Signature Mocha Frappe
items.description: Experience the irresistible allure of a Signature Mocha Frappe, where velvety chocolate meets aromatic espresso, blended to perfection with creamy milk and crowned with a swirl of whipped cream, offering a decadent and refreshing indulgence in every sip.

items.name: Caramel Frappe
items.description: Indulge in a creamy blend of espresso and caramel, crowned with whipped cream and drizzled with caramel sauce—a sweet escape in every sip. "Sip into bliss with every caramel swirl."

items.name: Cookie Monster Mocha Frappe
items.description: Embark on a deliciously wild ride with the Cookies Monster Mocha Frappe, where velvety chocolate meets chunks of irresistible cookies, blended to icy perfection, delivering a sweet and satisfying treat that's sure to satisfy your cravings and spark joy with every sip.

items.name: Seasonal Special Frappe
items.description: Embrace the flavors of the season with our tantalizing Seasonal Special Frappe, blending creamy textures with a burst of seasonal ingredients, creating a refreshing and delightful treat that captures the essence of each moment.

items.name: Passion Fruit Iced Tea
items.description: Quench your thirst with a tropical burst of tangy passion fruit infused into refreshing iced tea, creating a vibrant and invigorating beverage that transports you to sun-drenched paradise with each sip.

items.name: Blueberry Iced Tea
items.description: Cool off with the refreshing taste of blueberries infused into a crisp and invigorating iced tea, offering a delightful balance of sweet fruitiness and brisk tea notes in every sip, perfect for a sunny day refreshment.

items.name: Strawberry Iced Tea
items.description: Quench your thirst with the refreshing allure of Strawberry Iced Tea, where the tangy sweetness of ripe strawberries meets the cool embrace of chilled tea, crafting a revitalizing beverage bursting with fruity delight.

items.name: Peach Iced Tea
items.description: "Refreshingly sweet and tangy peach flavors dance in every sip of our Peach Iced Tea, a delightful blend of sun-ripened peaches and crisp tea leaves. Savor the sweetness of summer with every sip."

items.name: Berryblast Iced Tea
items.description: Quench your thirst with Berryblast Iced Tea, a refreshing infusion of ripe berries harmonized with the coolness of ice, offering a burst of fruity delight in every sip, perfect for a sunny day's rejuvenation.

items.name: Mango Iced Tea
items.description: "Indulge in the refreshing fusion of sweet mango and cool tea with our Mango Iced Tea—a delightful sip of summer in every glass. Savor the tropical twist, refreshment redefined."

items.name: Honey Mint Green Tea
items.description: "Savor the refreshing fusion of delicate green tea infused with the sweetness of honey and the invigorating essence of mint. A soothing elixir to rejuvenate your senses and uplift your spirits."

items.name: Hibiscus Cinnamon
items.description: "Savor the invigorating blend of hibiscus petals and green tea, delicately infused with the warmth of cinnamon, for a soothing and aromatic hot beverage experience."

items.name: Kashmiri Kahwa Kesar
items.description: Indulge in the aromatic allure of Kashmiri Kahwa, a tantalizing blend of saffron-infused hot tea, enriched with delicate spices, promising a soul-warming experience like no other. Embark on a sensory journey with each sip, as the golden hues of saffron dance gracefully amidst the comforting embrace of traditional Kashmiri flavors.

items.name: Chamomile Green Tea
items.description: "Savor the soothing blend of delicate chamomile flowers and refreshing green tea, a harmonious fusion to calm the senses and invigorate the spirit."

items.name: Blue Sky
items.description: "Refreshing and vibrant blue sky mojito, a tropical twist on a classic cocktail. Sip into the azure bliss and let every sip be your ticket to a beachside paradise."

items.name: Lavendar
items.description: "Indulge in the refreshing fusion of zesty lime and fragrant lavender, a tantalizing twist on the classic mojito. Escape to a world of relaxation with every sip - Lavender Mojito: Where tranquility meets zest."

items.name: Spicy Guava
items.description: "Experience a tantalizing twist with our Spicy Guava Mojito, blending the refreshing essence of guava with a kick of spice. Savor the zest of the tropics in every sip. Ignite your taste buds with a fiery fusion of flavor."

items.name: Pink Lemonade
items.description: "Indulge in a refreshing twist with our Pink Lemonade Mojito, blending zesty lemon, sweet strawberries, and minty freshness for a vibrant sip of summer. Sip, savor, and let the pink hues of paradise dance on your palate." #SavorThePinkTwist

items.name: Spicy Pineapple
items.description: "Indulge in a tantalizing twist with our Spicy Pineapple Mojito, where zesty pineapple meets a fiery kick of spice, perfect for a refreshing escape. Heat up your happy hour with a tropical twist!"

items.name: Orange Citrus
items.description: "Refreshing Orange Citrus Mojito: A zesty twist on the classic with tangy oranges, fresh mint, and a splash of citrus, creating the perfect balance of flavors. Sip into sunshine with every delightful sip!"

items.name: Sky Red
items.description: "Indulge in the vibrant allure of a Sky Red Mojito, where zesty lime meets the exotic sweetness of Curacao, delivering a taste that paints the town red with refreshment."

items.name: Orange Citrus Smoothie
items.description: "Indulge in a zesty whirlwind of sunshine with our Orange Citrus milkshake – a vibrant fusion that dances on your taste buds like a citrus orchestra. It's a sip of pure joy that'll make you question why oranges ever settled for just being squeezed."

items.name: Strawberry Smoothie
items.description: Embark on a refreshing journey with a strawberry smoothie, blending luscious strawberries with milk to create a vibrant and satisfying burst of fruity goodness that invigorates the senses with each sip.

items.name: Blueberry Smoothie
items.description: A refreshing blend of plump, ripe blueberries, this vibrant smoothie bursts with antioxidants and irresistible fruity goodness, making it the perfect wholesome treat for any time of day.

items.name: Berry Blast Smoothie
items.description: Indulge in the refreshing taste of ripe strawberries blended to perfection with dairy-free alternatives, creating a luscious and nutritious smoothie bursting with fruity goodness and vibrant flavors.

items.name: Passion Fruit Smoothie
items.description: Embark on a tantalizing journey with the Passion Fruit smoothie, where the tangy zest of yuzu meets the tropical sweetness of passion fruit, creating a refreshing and invigorating blend that's bursting with vibrant flavors.

items.name: Papa Bear Signature Smoothie
items.description: The House Blend Signature smoothie offers a symphony of flavors, blending ripe tropical fruits with ice for a refreshingly smooth and satisfying treat that's bursting with vitality in every sip.

items.name: Double Brownie Milk Shakes
items.description: Indulge in the ultimate decadence with our Double Brownie Milkshake - a rich blend of creamy chocolate ice cream and fudgy brownie pieces, delivering twice the delight in every sip. Satisfy your sweet cravings with a swirl of perfection in every shake.

items.name: Red Velvet Cheesecake Milk Shakes
items.description: Indulge in decadence with our Red Velvet Cheesecake milkshake, a creamy fusion of rich red velvet cake and luscious cheesecake blended to perfection. Satisfy your sweet cravings with every sip - a symphony of flavors in a single shake.

items.name: Tiramisu Milk Shakes
items.description: Indulge in the creamy delight of a Tiramisu milkshake, blending rich espresso, velvety mascarpone, and hints of cocoa into a heavenly sip. Elevate your shake game with every decadent slurp, a sweet escape to Italian bliss.

items.name: Hazelnut Milk Shakes
items.description: Indulge in the creamy decadence of a hazelnut milkshake, where smooth hazelnut flavors dance with velvety milk, creating a luscious and satisfying treat that's both comforting and delightfully nutty.

items.name: Kitkat Milk Shakes
items.description: Indulge in a creamy symphony of crushed KitKat bars blended with chilled milk, offering a decadent twist on a classic treat that satisfies both chocolate cravings and milkshake desires in one delightful sip.

items.name: Biscoff Milk Shakes
items.description: Indulge in the creamy delight of a Biscoff milkshake, blending smooth vanilla ice cream with the irresistible taste of caramelized cookies. "Sip into sweetness with every spoonful."

items.name: Oreomilk Shakes
items.description: Indulge in the ultimate creamy treat with an Oreo milkshake, blending velvety vanilla ice cream with crushed Oreo cookies for a delectable fusion of sweetness and crunch, guaranteed to satisfy every craving in a single sip.

items.name: Seasonal Fruit Milk Shakes
items.description: "Indulge in a symphony of seasonal fruits dancing in creamy harmony, where every sip whispers a tale of orchard bliss. It's not just a milkshake; it's a fruity fiesta that'll make your taste buds do the tango!"

items.name: Rocher Milk Shakes
items.description: Indulge in the velvety embrace of Rocher chocolate, swirled into a milkshake so divine, every sip whispers sweet secrets to your taste buds. Because why settle for ordinary when you can sip on decadence with a crunch?

items.name: Mixed Berry Milk Shakes
items.description: "Indulge in a symphony of summer's sweetness with our Mixed Berry milkshake, where every sip is a berrylicious dance on your taste buds. Get ready to shake up your senses and berry-fy your day!"

items.name: Classic Pb
items.description: Indulge in nostalgia with our Classic Milkshake, where every sip whispers tales of yesteryears. It's a delicious time machine in a frosty glass, bringing smiles as timeless as its flavor.

items.name: Caramel Milk Shakes
items.description: Indulge in the sweet symphony of caramel kissed with cream, a milkshake so divine it'll make your taste buds dance with delight—sip away your worries, one creamy caramel swirl at a time.

items.name: Strawberry Cheesecake Milk Shakes
items.description: "Indulge in a whirlwind of creamy delight and fruity bliss with our Strawberry Cheesecake Milkshake, where every sip is a slice of happiness. Warning: May cause spontaneous cravings and envy among bystanders."

items.name: Classic New York Cheesecake
items.description: Indulge in the decadent delight of New York cheesecake, featuring a creamy, velvety texture atop a buttery graham cracker crust, perfectly balanced with a hint of tanginess, offering a luxurious dessert experience that captivates the palate with each heavenly bite.

items.name: Green Matcha Cheesecake
items.description: "Indulge in a tantalizing dance of flavors with our Green Matcha cheesecake, where creamy decadence meets the vibrant embrace of Japanese green tea. One bite, and you'll realize: this dessert isn't just a treat; it's a zen moment in every forkful."

items.name: Nutty Hazelnut Cheesecake
items.description: Indulge in a decadent Nutty Hazelnut cheesecake, where every creamy bite is a nut lover's dream. It's a slice of heaven that'll have you saying, "Who needs a spoon when you've got hazelnuts to swoon?"

items.name: Milky Kitkat Cheesecake
items.description: Indulge in the creamy delight of Milky Kitkat cheesecake, where velvety smoothness meets the irresistible crunch of Kitkat bars, delivering a slice of pure euphoria. One bite, and you'll be reaching for the stars with every heavenly mouthful!

items.name: Mr. Rocher Cheesecake
items.description: Indulge in decadent delight with Mr. Bear Rocher cheesecake, where creamy chocolate meets crunchy hazelnuts. It's a hug from dessert heaven that'll leave you beary satisfied!

items.name: Creamy Biscoff Cheesecake
items.description: Indulge in layers of velvety Biscoff-infused creaminess atop a crumbly biscuit base—because every slice is a ticket to sweet serenity that craves no explanation, only adoration.

items.name: Classic Brownie
items.description: Indulge in the timeless allure of our Classic Brownie, where rich chocolate meets irresistible cakey perfection. One bite, and you'll realize why some classics never go out of style.

items.name: Nutella Brownie
items.description: Indulge in a decadent Nutella brownie, where every bite is a blissful swirl of chocolate ecstasy. It's the sweetest way to turn any day into a celebration of cocoa dreams!

items.name: Biscoff Brownie
items.description: The cookie spread that turns your toast into a gourmet indulgence, making every breakfast a cookie-lover's dream come true. Spread the love, one biscuit at a time!

items.name: Red Velvet Cream Cheese Brownie
items.description: Indulge in decadent layers of rich red velvet and creamy cheesecake atop a fudgy brownie base—a divine symphony of flavors in every bite. "Savor the bliss of heavenly layers, where red velvet meets creamy delight in every irresistible square."

items.name: Chef Papa's Mocha Brownie
items.description: Indulge in Chef Papa's decadent Mocha Brownie, where rich cocoa meets aromatic espresso for an irresistible fusion of flavors. "Savor every bite, where chocolate and coffee collide in perfect harmony."

items.name: Pesto Spaghetti
items.description: "Savor the vibrant flavors of summer with our Pesto Spaghetti Salad: a harmonious blend of al dente spaghetti, fresh basil pesto, and crisp vegetables, perfect for a quick and satisfying meal on the go."
